public static enum GoConstants.NumberingMode
extends java.lang.Enum<GoConstants.NumberingMode>
implements lib.NameProvider

NumberingMode encapsulates most of the behavior associated with choosing how move numbers are displayed on stones. This enum also serves as a singleton class with a selected value with the ability to display a menu of choices.
